These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Transport: tram, snowmobile, skateboard, trike
1. Transport:trike is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Transport:snowmobile##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Transport:skateboard is on the left or right of Transport:trike##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Transport        | tram | snowmobile   | trike | skateboard    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Transport: scooter, snowmobile, bike, bus
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Transport:scooter is on the left of Transport:bike##1
3. Transport:bike is in an odd position##4
4. Transport:scooter == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Transport:snowmobile is on the right of Transport:bike##1
6. Transport:scooter == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Transport   | bus    | scooter | bike | snowmobile    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Game: domino, poker, scrabble, monopoly
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Game:monopoly is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Game:scrabble is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Game:poker##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Game:poker is on the right of Game:scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Game          | monopoly | scrabble | poker    | domino      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
City: new-york, liverpool, edinburgh, san-francisco
1. Hobby:drawing is between City:new-york and City:san-francisco##2
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Hobby:cooking##1
3. City:edinburgh is in an odd position##4
4. City:liverpool is on the left of City:san-francisco##1
5. City:liverpool is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| City   | edinburgh       | new-york   | liverpool    | san-francisco  |

