.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Movie-Genre: drama, animation, comedy, disaster
Nationality: american, australian, indian, russian
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the right of Nationality:russian##1
2. Nationality:australian == Movie-Genre:disaster##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Movie-Genre:drama##1
4. Movie-Genre:animation is on the far left##1
5. Movie-Genre:comedy is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | drama    | comedy   | disaster       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

