.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Food: pineapple, cauliflower, nectarine, asparagus
Music-Genre: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. Food:pineapple == Music-Genre:jazz##1
2. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Food:pineapple##1
3. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:disco and Food:nectarine##2
4. Food:pineapple is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco##3
6. Food:cauliflower is on the left or right of Music-Genre:dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Food      | cauliflower       | nectarine   | pineapple | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

