2. Transport:boat is on the far left or far right##3
3. Transport:airplane is on the left of Sport:weightlifting##1
4. Transport:motorbike is on the left of Transport:airplane##1
5. Sport:weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:skateboarding##1

