2. Sport:ice-hockey == Transport:taxi##1
3. Sport:cricket == Transport:trike##1
4. Transport:airplane is on the left or right of Transport:trike##3
5. Transport:taxi is in an even position##4
6. Transport:airplane is on the right of Sport:ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Transport   | subway | taxi | airplane    | trike |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

