.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
House: farmhouse, colonial, victorian, futuristic
Food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. Food:kale is on the far left##1
2. House:victorian is on the left or right of House:farmhouse##3
3. House:futuristic is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the right of House:farmhouse##1
6. Food:pepper is in an even position##4
7. Food:corn == House:colonial##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse    | victorian       | colonial |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

